The paper deals with the problem of multi-class relational sequence learning using feature construction and selection methods. This problem is closely related to machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI), natural language processing and computational linguistics (cs.CL), cryptography and security (cs.CR), and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
